wow...its been a long time since ive written last...but yeah whatever ive just been living life as it comes...its been weird...good yet bad...and very confusing...blah...i dont feel like writing a lot right now...so...ive been kinda an ass to emily...but not real bad...just walking away from her and not really talking...but i dont talk much anyway...i want to talk to her but we've not really ever alone...*sigh* i wanted to talk to her today on AiM but kali was over...meh...im kinda depressed right now...but im talking to emily so...happy happy i guess...well g2g now...im supposed to talk to emily more...so ill be more happy and shit like that...well bye!

well um...i guess ill write i little more than what i did last time...since its been so long...(damn old people dont let me use the computer) 
ok...so whats new...*thinks*...nothing really...oh...wait no...OH! yeah theres one thing im going out with Emily now...oooOOOO...so for all you stupid people kat and me broke up a while ago so um...yeah
blah...well i went to the park today...i mean yesterday...bahahahaha! ok that wasnt funny...but whatever it was pretty fun...lets see...who was there...Emily, me, Veronica, Anthony, Cody, Andre, and um...Jackie...right yeah sure whatever
But than everyone left earlier so at like 7 or so Emily and me left and walked over to Kali's (my cousin) and we hung out there for a bit before she had to go...well when she left i played some Dragon Ball Z 2 and owned Kia, god damn im good at that game mwahahahaha I OWN YOU! 
Then at like 10 i came home and got on the computer cuz i was bored...but now im going to go cuz its 2:00 am and im hungry.
i just saw i was still on yahoo...and yahoo sucks!!
heh 'saw' is 'was' backwards thats cool...wow...im weird
i got to do that survey thingy that emily sent me...ill do it tomorrow...im mean today...wait...later today mwahahaha
well 'night 'night to you people that read this

meh...i havent been writing...i think i might get a xanga thing...i dunno...seems like the new thing...but im not really into being with everyone else...too hard to keep up with the new shit every 3 seconds. well...blah...nothing has really happened...Kat and me have been good...nothing exciting happened to me...well i got marks AiM sn...but he doesnt talk much...heh he asked if i wanted to be in his band...i think...it seemed like thats what he was asking, i dunno. ive been playing gunbound, failed fate 0 and runescape...fate fate and runescape get kinda boring after a while. but Kramer (Robert) got to play gunbound finally like last week and ive been doing pretty good with that shit. hm...lets see what else...school starts in about a week...woohoo...blah. well its kinda good...i get to see my friends. fuck...i really need to change at school and do my work...fuck i dont want to fail that shit...besides i have plans after school and i dont want to mess them up. maybe ill put a link to this thing in my AiM profile. its the only way anyone would read it. ha marks telling me to start my comic again. well im going to go now...peace! 

-Mushroom
